$OpenBSD: patch-runtime_CMakeLists_txt,v 1.1.1.1 2021/11/21 13:51:47 bcallah Exp $

Set proper DFLAGS.
Make sure C parts are built as PIC.

Index: runtime/CMakeLists.txt
--- runtime/CMakeLists.txt.orig
+++ runtime/CMakeLists.txt
